title: The Anthony Cumia Show 2014-08-27
description: Ant starts the show revisiting Miley Cyrus at the VMA's and her "homeless movie star," we see a few clips of real homeless guys, watch two horrendous "ice bucket challenge" videos, and listen in on a couple of calls. We learn about a new apology given by ESPN, talk Uzi's, Chelsea Handler leaving late night TV, and we catch a glimpse of Chip Chipperson. Chip then calls into the hotline, Ant takes a few more calls, and we end the show with a video that Nick DiPaolo suggested.
